 (file format)|tar]] archive format. |- |''' <[[C Programming/POSIX Reference/termios.h|termios.h]]>''' || Allows [[Serial port|terminal I/O]] interfaces. |- |''' <[[C Programming/POSIX Reference/unistd.h|unistd.h]]>''' || Various essential POSIX functions and constants. |- |''' <[[C Programming/POSIX Reference/utime.h|utime.h]]>''' || [[inode]] access and modification times. |}
